title: Top al-Qaeda commander killed in airstrike in Syria
text:
Published By: Philly News Nation/World - Today 
BEIRUT - An airstrike has killed a top al-Qaeda commander and two other fighters in Syria, activists said Saturday, but it was not immediate...
